<body>
  <h1>Delete Your IntelliX Account</h1>
  <p>If you have an IntelliX account and wish to delete it, please follow the instructions below.</p>

  <h2>How to Request Deletion</h2>
  <p>Email us at <strong>support@epteck.com</strong> from your registered account email with the subject: <em>“Delete My IntelliX Account”</em>.</p>

  <h2>What Will Be Deleted?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Your account information (name, email, password)</li>
    <li>Associated IoT device configurations</li>
    <li>Usage logs and historical data</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We do not retain any personal data after deletion. Backups are retained for up to 30 days for recovery and legal compliance.</p>

  <h2>Need Help?</h2>
  <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@epteck.com">support@epteck.com</a></p>
</body>
